{
  "video_id": "VOVmVMJEhg8",
  "title": "The Ecstasy of Curiosity",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 18562.0,
      "end_time": 20270.0,
      "text": "So I came across this idea the other day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 20270.0,
      "end_time": 22186.0,
      "text": "I think it was Aristotle who put it out there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22186.0,
      "end_time": 24730.0,
      "text": "but it was this notion that human beings"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24730.0,
      "end_time": 26550.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t care about spectacle."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26550.0,
      "end_time": 30740.0,
      "text": "What they care about is ecstatic understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30740.0,
      "end_time": 33540.0,
      "text": "Understanding, comprehension."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33540.0,
      "end_time": 37090.0,
      "text": "In other words, cognitive ecstasy"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37090.0,
      "end_time": 39930.0,
      "text": "defined as an exhilarating neuro storm"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39930.0,
      "end_time": 43110.0,
      "text": "of intense intellectual pleasure."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43110.0,
      "end_time": 45515.0,
      "text": "The book &quot;The Ravenous Brain&quot; talks about this idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45515.0,
      "end_time": 48810.0,
      "text": "that consciousness is obsessed with pattern."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48810.0,
      "end_time": 52170.0,
      "text": "Pattern is structure, structure amidst"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52170.0,
      "end_time": 54900.0,
      "text": "the chaos, a signal in the noise."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54900.0,
      "end_time": 58670.0,
      "text": "And when we find patterns, when we connect the dots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58670.0,
      "end_time": 63000.0,
      "text": "we experience this cognitive ecstasy, this exhilarating"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63000.0,
      "end_time": 64030.0,
      "text": "neuro storm."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64030.0,
      "end_time": 66373.0,
      "text": "And we get children, they&#39;re young,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66373.0,
      "end_time": 67956.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re learning all the time, they&#39;re"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67956.0,
      "end_time": 69025.0,
      "text": "creating new synaptic connections."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69025.0,
      "end_time": 71470.0,
      "text": "They experience this cognitive ecstasy, this curiosity."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71470.0,
      "end_time": 76705.0,
      "text": "This insatiable drive to understand is on fire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 76705.0,
      "end_time": 79250.0,
      "text": "is fervor, is [? feral ?] in little kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79250.0,
      "end_time": 82390.0,
      "text": "Imagine the first time you look at a microscope."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82390.0,
      "end_time": 85210.0,
      "text": "You see that cosmos-- revealed for the first time--"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85210.0,
      "end_time": 86490.0,
      "text": "of the microscopic."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86490.0,
      "end_time": 88440.0,
      "text": "When you look through a telescope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88440.0,
      "end_time": 92420.0,
      "text": "and you all of a sudden see the cosmos of the macroscopic."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92420.0,
      "end_time": 96170.0,
      "text": "Perhaps the best line was Ross Anderson&#39;s description"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96170.0,
      "end_time": 101050.0,
      "text": "of the ontological awakening provided by the Hubble Space"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101050.0,
      "end_time": 104130.0,
      "text": "telescope&#39;s images of the deep field."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104130.0,
      "end_time": 107890.0,
      "text": "He said, &quot;Through the sheer aesthetic force"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107890.0,
      "end_time": 111070.0,
      "text": "of its discoveries, the Hubble distilled"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111070.0,
      "end_time": 115110.0,
      "text": "the complex abstractions of astrophysics"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 115110.0,
      "end_time": 120140.0,
      "text": "into singular expressions of color and light,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 120140.0,
      "end_time": 123280.0,
      "text": "vindicating Keats&#39; famous couplet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123280.0,
      "end_time": 127309.0,
      "text": "&quot;Beauty is truth, truth beauty.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 127309.0,
      "end_time": 129100.0,
      "text": "The sad part, as Sir Kenneth Robinson says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 129100.0,
      "end_time": 131780.0,
      "text": "is that we lose this as we grow up."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 131780.0,
      "end_time": 134620.0,
      "text": "Our educational institutions are failing us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134620.0,
      "end_time": 137620.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re not providing the context for this curiosity"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 137620.0,
      "end_time": 141560.0,
      "text": "to explode, to continue to emerge indefinitely."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141560.0,
      "end_time": 143760.0,
      "text": "Instead we slowly die."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143760.0,
      "end_time": 146110.0,
      "text": "And I think our goal is to create media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146110.0,
      "end_time": 148950.0,
      "text": "to create content, to create spaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 148950.0,
      "end_time": 152460.0,
      "text": "that allow us to stay curious, to stay alive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152460.0,
      "end_time": 155270.0,
      "text": "to awaken the wonder junkie in all of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155270.0,
      "end_time": 160770.0,
      "text": "to unleash the brave, reckless gods within us all."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 160770.0,
      "end_time": 162210.0,
      "text": "That is my goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 162210.0,
      "end_time": 164470.0,
